one_reviews_text: this game is so freakin fun! u get too see miku dance and basically dance along with her i thing the rythm is on point as well its great for miku fans and people that just love the rythm of her songs!!

So far the worst  VR rhythm game I played. Callingit rhythm game is actualy streaching it, since you dont need to have any sence of rhythm. All you do is swing your arms to touch swarm of rings going in your direction. The only good point of this game is that it looks good, even though its quite old game.
